---
title: Cheesy Chicken & Guacamole Tortas Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Looking for a dynamic dinner? Meet the torta! Our take on this classic Mexican sandwich starts with crusty ciabatta bread slathered with savory spiced mashed beans layered with cheesy fajita-spiced chicken, juicy tomato, and a layer of creamy guac. With a tangy pico de gallo-studded spring mix salad and crunchy chips, this 15-minute (!) super-stuffed sammie + salad is torta-lly dinner worthy!
